src:
Nexam Chemical presenterar det tredje kvartalet 2019 den 12 november kl. 11:00
Den 12 november 2019 kl. 08:30 publicerar Nexam Chemical sin delårsrapport för det tredje kvartalet 2019. Rapporten och presentationen kommer att finnas tillgänglig på bolagets hemsida.
06 Nov 2019, 10:30 by Nexam Chemical

text:
Nexam Chemical will present the third quarter of 2019 on 12 November at. 11:00
On November 12, 2019 at At 08:30, Nexam Chemical will publish its interim report for the third quarter of 2019. The report and presentation will be available on the company's website.
Nov 06, 2019, 10:30 am by Nexam Chemical
